## ✅ Accessibility Features

All form elements follow **WCAG** accessibility standards:

- Every `<input>`, `<select>`, and `<textarea>` has:
  - A matching `<label for="id">` — screen reader support
  - A unique `id` attribute
  - A `title` attribute — tooltip on hover
- Radio groups use `<fieldset>` + `<legend>` (Gender)
- Yes/No radio groups use `role="radiogroup"` + `aria-labelledby`
- Hidden labels use `.sr-only` class (visually hidden, screen reader visible)
- Sections use `aria-labelledby` for landmark navigation
- Office checkboxes use `role="group"` + `aria-label`

